,"jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9M0","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/15\/sujud-sajdah-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":37572,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Allah expiates sins by prostration in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo servant prostrates for the sake of Allah but that Allah will record for him one good deed, erase one bad deed, and raise his status by a degree. Thus, perform many prostrations.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17071,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/01\/sujud-sajdah-darajah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37572,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Each prostration rewarded by a degree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo servant prostrates for the sake of Allah but that Allah will raise his status by a degree and expiate one of his sins.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 388 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0630\u0631 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/sajdah-salat-not-like-kalb\/","url_meta":{"origin":37572,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Keep forearms raised in prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe straight in prostration and let none of you put his forearms on the ground like a dog.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 788, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 493 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33615,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/sujud-sajdah-more-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37572,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Prostrate more to be with the Prophet in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Rabi\u2019ah ibn Ka\u2019b reported: I spent the night with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and I brought him water for his ablution and his needs. The Prophet said to me, \u201cAsk.\u201d I said, \u201cI ask for your companionship in Paradise.\u201d The Prophet said, \"And anything\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17544,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/nearest-allah-sujud-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":37572,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: You are nearest to Allah in prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe servant is closest to his Lord during prostration, so increase your supplications therein.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 482 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0628\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35581,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/06\/istighfar-sujood\/","url_meta":{"origin":37572,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Ask Allah&#8217;s forgiveness in prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to say in his prostration, \u201cO Allah, forgive all of my sins, the small and large, the first and last, the public and private.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 483 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &qu